Package ui

package ui
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    RunnableCheckCondition
    Lambda used to check if a condition is true or not.
    RunnableGetListItems<T>
    Lambda for requesting the items in a list.
    RunnableInputFinish
    Lambda used for when InputMenu has finished getting all of it's inputs.
    RunnableSelectListItem<T>
    Lambda used for when a user has selected an item in OptionListMenu.
    RunnableSelectOption
    Lambda used for an associated MenuOption has been selected.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ANSICodes
    Wrapper class containing all ANSI Codes used in the project.
    InformationMenu
    Menu to show the user information without the need to prompt input from them.
    InputMenu
    Class extending Menu that adds the option of prompting the user for input for object creation.
    Menu
    Abstract class that represents a menu in the user interface.
    MenuInput
    Datastructure used by InputMenu to store information about the input the menu should ask for.
    MenuInputInt
    Extension of MenuInput that requires the input to be an integer.
    MenuInputOptions
    Datastructure used by InputMenu for menu inputs where an option is desired.
    MenuOption
    Datastructure used by OptionMenu representing an option that can be chosen in a menu.
    MenuQuickInput
    Menu for requesting a single of input from the user quickly, without the need for a callback function.
    OptionListMenu<T extends Listable>
    OptionMenu for selecting an item from a arraylist.
    OptionMenu
    Menu in which options are given that the user can choose from.
    OptionMenuWithResult<T>
    Extension of OptionMenu that includes storing a result field.
    OptionMenuYesNo
    Option menu for simple yes/no choices.
